sellerCard.oneLiner: SkyRocket Your Business With SEM Expert
sellerCard.description:
Hello! 

This is SEM EXPERT, a professional digital marketer and web developer with extensive experience in managing Google Ads, Facebook Ads, and Amazon Ads. 

I specialize in providing on-page, technical, and monthly SEO services to enhance online visibility effectively. 

Moreover, I offer tailored website development solutions utilizing WordPress, Shopify, Wix, Squarespace, and others. 

I would be delighted to collaborate to help grow your business and achieve your objectives.

Let's get started right now!

Thank you.

description.content:
Are you looking for a professional Wix developer to create or redesign your Wix website or online store? You're in the right place!


I am a certified Wix expert with years of experience in Wix website design and development. Whether you need a fresh Wix design for a brand-new site or a complete revamp to refresh your online presence, I can help you bring your vision to life.



What Services I'll Provide You in This Gig:


  • Custom Wix Site Design
  • Complete Clone of Your Existing Site
  • Wix Online Store Setup for Ecommerce
  • Full Integration With Wix Studio for Advanced Features
  • Website Redesign to Optimize and Modernize Your Site
  • Revamp Wix Website to Improve Functionality & User Experience
  • Creation & Customization of Wix Store for Online Selling



Why Choose Me?


  1. Wix Expert | High-Quality Work
  2. On-Time Delivery | After Delivery Support
  3. Constant Communication | 100% Satisfaction


Whether you need a brand-new Wix website or want to recreate your existing one, I am here to assist you in creating a professional online presence.


Let's collaborate to make your Wix online store stand out!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What are the necessary requirements that I have to provide?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: For Your WIX website, we need your website Logo, your page names and their contents, social media links if you have any, Your business details, and pictures (if you don't have any, I will provide you with Some Free pictures related to your website.)

questionsAndAnswers.question: May I know who is the hosting provider of this business mail?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No! I don’t provide a domain and Wix subscription plan. You have to buy a domain and purchase a Wix subscription plan, and I can offer my assistance in connecting with your premium plan Wix website!

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many Revisions will you offer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: As we have mentioned above, we will accept “UNLIMITED” revisions until the client is satisfied, and after the project, we will provide full support for your website's issues.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer help after project completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I totally do that with all my clients. Should you find yourself in a pickle after the project is complete, I can offer some guidance.

reviews.comment: We feel like our vision about the website did not get through as we wanted. The delivery took longer than expected because of this. However he made sure to do his best with our instructions and he kept working until we felt that it was good enough. Overall he did he’s absolut best to meet our needs.

seller_response.comment: Thank you for your kind words! I truly appreciate your patience throughout the process. I'm glad we were able to work together to bring your vision to life, and I’m happy that the final result met your expectations. It was a pleasure working with you!

reviews.comment: Wow! Semexpert did an amazing job creating the perfect author website for me. He was very responsive to my needs and happily addressed my changes and corrections immediately.  To top it off, my order was delivered ahead of the due date. Thank you, Semexpert for a job well done!

seller_response.comment: Thanks very much for the Tip!! Really appreciated. Looking forward to the next order.

reviews.comment: Great work! He designed a Wix website that is sleek, professional, and perfectly tailored to my brand. The site is easy to navigate and has helped elevate my online presence.

seller_response.comment: Thanks, I'm glad you got what you wanted. I would love to work with you again.

reviews.comment:
Great lack of understanding the task. Created a site that could not be used as he didn't understand that making products as blogposts means manual work from here on out. Useless work and have to do it all myself now anyway. 

Would not recommend.

seller_response.comment:
Thanks for your feedback.

I have completed the project based on my understanding and our multiple discussions regarding the requirements. We had several meetings about the project, and finally, you requested a dynamic page. Unfortunately, due to Wix’s limitations, I couldn’t implement it that way. However, I am providing you with an alternative solution—please let me know if you agree, and I will proceed accordingly.

I have followed your instructions carefully, and I don’t believe I have delivered something unusable. My priority is always client satisfaction.

If you still need any modifications, please let me know—I am happy to make the necessary adjustments.

reviews.comment: Unable to think proactively about responsiveness for an easy 6-page website. Not kept to delivery deadline. Does not check own work before delivery. Not recommended to work with. Waste of time.

seller_response.comment:
Thank you for your feedback. 

From the start of the project, I’ve worked according to my commitment and kept you updated on every task. Before project delivery, I provided you with a complete update, including my approach to the delivery. If you need any changes, I encouraged you to let me know, but I didn’t receive any feedback until now. I’m not sure why you’re dissatisfied with my work.

Additionally, I clearly stated that I’m available for help after delivery, as client satisfaction is my top priority.
